title: Henrikh Mkhitaryan’s brilliant Man United moment will take some beating - Mark Lawrenson
text:
Man Utd via Getty Images 1 of 12 Who impressed for Manchester United against Blackburn? He got his head up and there won’t be a better pass played in the FA Cup all weekend Mark Lawrenson 
“Mkhitaryan thought at first he would get clattered, but he nicked it past the player,” Lawrenson told Match of the Day . 
“He got his head up and there won’t be a better pass played in the FA Cup all weekend. 
“There hasn’t been so far unless Sutton come up with something against Arsenal.” 
Mkhitaryan was awarded Man of the match for his display. Related articles
